{
  "stem": "9503.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then my husband finally told them, you know, Judy was in this camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She can't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were-- I mean, it would have been a lot better if I would have said why I couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it-- it really-- it's-- it remained an unfinished business for a long, long time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It came up again in a totally unexpected form when one of my kids started having some difficulties leaving the house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at that point, I was told to go for some help, which I did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And at that point, I got, again, this rage that I had this time with the German soldiers of this isn't fair.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, here we go again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had-- you know, what is this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've made a-- a line under it already, and you know, how dare this come back again?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I remember thinking that the Germans won after all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They won by having those killed that they killed and those maimed that survived and that they really had won the battle.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So at that point, I-- I had need for some intensive therapy, and we weren't in a position to foot those bills.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is-- at that point, I finally [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] relented the-- the request that my uncle in Holland had been making year after year to file for restitution.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I thought for us to go broke and have this happen to the children, this-- this reaction, that just isn't right.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So then I thought I'm going to get out of Germany whatever I can.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But on the other hand, for instance, even now I was invited by the city that my mom comes from, Montabaur, to visit.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
